---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import BackButton from "../components/BackButton.astro";
import ContactButton from "../components/ContactButton.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import helmImg from "../assets/images/about-helm-inspection.png";
import engineImg from "../assets/images/about-engine-room.png";
---

<Layout
  title="About Captain Olivier"
  description="Meet Captain Olivier — a seasoned yacht captain with decades of experience from the South of France to South Florida."
  noBackground={true}
>
  <div class="about-bg"></div>

  <div class="about-page">
    <div class="about-top">
      <BackButton href="/" />
    </div>

    <h1>About Captain Olivier</h1>

    <div class="about-intro">
      <p>
        With decades of experience navigating the Mediterranean waters of the
        South of France and many years commanding vessels along the coast of
        South Florida, Captain Olivier brings a rare combination of
        Old-World craftsmanship and hands-on expertise to every yacht he manages.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-section">
      <div class="about-text">
        <h2>Hands-On Expertise</h2>
        <p>
          Captain Olivier is not your typical captain who stays behind the helm.
          He is deeply involved in every aspect of yacht care — from routine
          engine oil checks and coolant monitoring to chartplotter updates and
          navigation system calibration. His philosophy is simple: know your
          vessel inside and out, and she will never let you down.
        </p>
        <p>
          Every inspection is performed personally, with the same meticulous
          attention to detail that has earned him the trust of yacht owners on
          both sides of the Atlantic.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-image">
        <Image
          src={helmImg}
          alt="Captain Olivier performing engine inspections and helm navigation checks"
          quality={80}
          class="collage-img"
        />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="about-section reverse">
      <div class="about-text">
        <h2>Engineering & Mechanical Mastery</h2>
        <p>
          From bilge pump inspections and water intrusion prevention to
          monitoring complex engine systems, Captain Olivier's technical
          knowledge runs deep. He personally oversees every mechanical system
          on board — ensuring that pumps, filters, plumbing, and power plants
          are always in peak condition.
        </p>
        <p>
          His hands-on approach means potential issues are caught early, saving
          owners from costly repairs and unexpected downtime. Whether it's a
          Volvo Penta IPS system or classic diesel engines, Olivier has the
          experience and know-how to keep your vessel running flawlessly.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-image">
        <Image
          src={engineImg}
          alt="Engine room maintenance — bilge systems, plumbing, and Volvo Penta engines"
          quality={80}
          class="collage-img"
        />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="about-section centered">
      <div class="about-text wide">
        <h2>Customer Satisfaction First</h2>
        <p>
          At the heart of Grand Bleu Yachts is a commitment to customer
          satisfaction and genuine understanding of each owner's needs. Captain
          Olivier takes the time to listen, understand your expectations, and
          tailor every service to match your lifestyle. Whether you use your
          yacht every weekend or visit a few times a year, he ensures your
          vessel is always ready to go — polished, fueled, and waiting for you.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="about-section centered">
      <div class="about-text wide">
        <h2>From the Mediterranean to Florida</h2>
        <p>
          Captain Olivier began his career on the sun-drenched coasts of the
          South of France, where he honed his skills on a wide range of motor
          yachts and sailing vessels. After years mastering the Mediterranean,
          he brought his expertise to South Florida — a region he now calls
          home and where he has built a reputation for excellence in yacht
          management, delivery, and charter services.
        </p>
        <p>
          His international background gives him a unique perspective on yacht
          care, blending European precision with the practical demands of
          cruising the Bahamas, the Keys, and the East Coast.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <ContactButton />
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-bg {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(
      160deg,
      #012a5e 0%,
      var(--blue-dark) 30%,
      var(--blue-medium) 60%,
      #012a5e 100%
    );
    z-index: -1;
  }

  .about-page {
    padding: var(--spacing-xl) var(--spacing-xl) var(--spacing-2xl);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .about-top {
    width: 100%;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: flex-start;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
    color: var(--white);
    text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .about-intro {
    max-width: 700px;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2xl);
  }

  .about-intro p {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
    text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }

  .about-section {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--spacing-xl);
    width: 100%;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2xl);
  }

  .about-section.reverse {
    flex-direction: row-reverse;
  }

  .about-section.centered {
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .about-text {
    flex: 1;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--spacing-xl);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
  }

  .about-text.wide {
    max-width: 700px;
  }

  .about-text h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }

  .about-text p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.93);
    text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .about-text p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .about-image {
    flex: 1;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
  }

  .collage-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-page {
      padding: var(--spacing-md);
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    }

    .about-section,
    .about-section.reverse {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .about-image {
      width: 100%;
    }

    .about-text.wide {
      max-width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
